{"lineNumber":81797,"originalJapaneseLine":"　このままなら、確実にそうなるだろうな」","translatedEnglishLine":"If things continue as they are, it will surely happen.\""},{"lineNumber":81798,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ふむ……そういや、少し疑問なんだが……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hmm... now that you mention it, I have a bit of a question...\""},{"lineNumber":81799,"originalJapaneseLine":"「お前らって、どっちも魔人なのに、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"You guys are both demons, but"},{"lineNumber":81800,"originalJapaneseLine":"　魔人同士で戦争なんてするんだな」","translatedEnglishLine":"you’re having a war against each other.\""},{"lineNumber":81801,"originalJapaneseLine":"「そんなの人間だって同じだろう？","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Isn’t that the same as with humans?"},{"lineNumber":81802,"originalJapaneseLine":"　考えが違えば争いは起こるものだ」","translatedEnglishLine":"If thoughts differ, conflicts arise.\""},{"lineNumber":81803,"originalJapaneseLine":"「今回の場合は……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"In this case..."},{"lineNumber":81804,"originalJapaneseLine":"　誰が魔王になるかで争いが始まった」","translatedEnglishLine":"The conflict started over who would become the Demon King.\""},{"lineNumber":81805,"originalJapaneseLine":"「魔王ってのはアレだ。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"The Demon King is that. "},{"lineNumber":81806,"originalJapaneseLine":"　魔物と魔人連中の王様」","translatedEnglishLine":"The king of monsters and demons.\""},{"lineNumber":81807,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ま、ザックリ言ってしまえばそうだな」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Well, roughly speaking, that's it.\""},{"lineNumber":81808,"originalJapaneseLine":"「魔王とは絶対的な支配者。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"The Demon King is the absolute ruler."},{"lineNumber":81809,"originalJapaneseLine":"　全ての魔物、使徒、魔人を従える存在だ」","translatedEnglishLine":"One who commands all monsters, apostles, and demons.\""},{"lineNumber":81810,"originalJapaneseLine":"「その魔王である","translatedEnglishLine":"\"That Demon King,"},{"lineNumber":81811,"originalJapaneseLine":"　先代のガイ様がいた頃は平和で……","translatedEnglishLine":"the previous lord, Guy, was around, peace reigned..."},{"lineNumber":81812,"originalJapaneseLine":"　魔物界も統一されていた」","translatedEnglishLine":"and the monster realm was unified.\""},{"lineNumber":81813,"originalJapaneseLine":"「だが、ガイ様が亡くなり、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"But after Lord Guy passed away,"},{"lineNumber":81814,"originalJapaneseLine":"　魔王が空位となることで状況は変わった」","translatedEnglishLine":"the Demon King's seat became vacant, and the situation changed.\""},{"lineNumber":81815,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ガイ様の遺言で新たな魔王に任命された美樹様が、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Miki, who was appointed as the new Demon King according to Lord Guy's will,"},{"lineNumber":81816,"originalJapaneseLine":"　魔王就任を嫌がり、逃げ出してしまってな……","translatedEnglishLine":"disliked becoming the Demon King and ran away...\""},{"lineNumber":81817,"originalJapaneseLine":"「普通に暮らしてた女の子に無理矢理","translatedEnglishLine":"\"They tried to forcibly make a girl who had been living a normal life"},{"lineNumber":81818,"originalJapaneseLine":"　魔王やらせようとしたとかなんとか……","translatedEnglishLine":"the Demon King or something...\""},{"lineNumber":81819,"originalJapaneseLine":"　そりゃ逃げられるに決まってる」","translatedEnglishLine":"Of course she ran away.\""},{"lineNumber":81820,"originalJapaneseLine":"「がははは、それで魔人共が","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hahaha, that's why the demons"},{"lineNumber":81821,"originalJapaneseLine":"　大慌てならいい気味ってもんだ」","translatedEnglishLine":"were all panicked, serves them right.\""},{"lineNumber":81822,"originalJapaneseLine":"「いや……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"No..."},{"lineNumber":81823,"originalJapaneseLine":"　美樹様の逃亡の影響は、","translatedEnglishLine":"The impact of Lady Miki's escape,"},{"lineNumber":81824,"originalJapaneseLine":"　そんなものじゃ済まなかった」","translatedEnglishLine":"was far more serious than that.\""},{"lineNumber":81825,"originalJapaneseLine":"「なに？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"What?\""},{"lineNumber":81826,"originalJapaneseLine":"「魔王の空位。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"The vacancy of the Demon King's seat."},{"lineNumber":81827,"originalJapaneseLine":"　これを好機と見た魔人の一人である","translatedEnglishLine":"One demon who saw this as an opportunity,"},{"lineNumber":81828,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ケイブリスの馬鹿がよりにもよって――","translatedEnglishLine":"the fool Cavebliss, no less—"},{"lineNumber":81829,"originalJapaneseLine":"「自分が魔王になると、言い出した」","translatedEnglishLine":"declared that he would become the Demon King.\""},{"lineNumber":81830,"originalJapaneseLine":"「そんなガイ様の遺言に反すること、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Such an act against Lord Guy’s will,"},{"lineNumber":81831,"originalJapaneseLine":"　認められるものか！」","translatedEnglishLine":"can never be accepted!\""},{"lineNumber":81832,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ケイブリスなど無視して、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ignoring Cavebliss,"},{"lineNumber":81833,"originalJapaneseLine":"　美樹様を捜し出して魔王の座に就いて頂き、","translatedEnglishLine":"we must find Lady Miki and have her take the Demon King's throne,"},{"lineNumber":81834,"originalJapaneseLine":"　魔物界を統治してもらわなければ！」","translatedEnglishLine":"so she can govern the monster realm!\""},{"lineNumber":81835,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ホーネット様を中心とする、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Many demons and monsters, centered on Lord Hornet,"},{"lineNumber":81836,"originalJapaneseLine":"　多くの魔人と魔物がその気持ちでいたが……","translatedEnglishLine":"held that intention, but...\""},{"lineNumber":81837,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ケイブリスの奴の卑怯な策略で……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Through Cavebliss’s cowardly scheme,"},{"lineNumber":81838,"originalJapaneseLine":"　徐々にケイブリス側に魔人や魔物が増えていき、","translatedEnglishLine":"demons and monsters gradually joined Cavebliss's side,"},{"lineNumber":81839,"originalJapaneseLine":"　派閥は真っ二つに分かれ……","translatedEnglishLine":"and the factions split right down the middle..."},{"lineNumber":81840,"originalJapaneseLine":"「我ら魔人はついに全面戦争に至った……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"We demons ultimately ended up in all-out war...\""}]}

